Test.Name: All VEC doesn't support JPEG
Test.Description: All VEC doesn't support JPEG Check that thete is Warning in the test tool log Check that test tool will try to set jpeg for the first, middle anf last VECs DUT behaviour is incorrect: it is imposible to modify VEC to required encoding

Test.Name: One VEC supports JPEG
Test.Description: The second VEC supports JPEG Check that test tool will try to find/careate profile for the second VEC Check that test tool will not test the other VECs

Test.Name: More than 3 VECs support JPEG
Test.Description: The 2nd VEC supports JPEG The 3rd VEC supports JPEG The 4th VEC supports JPEG The 5th VEC supports JPEG Check that test tool will try to find/careate profile for three VECs: 2, 4 and 5. Check that test tool will not test the other VECs

Test.Name: All VEC doesn't support JPEG: the last VEC is changed to JPEG
Test.Description: All VEC doesn't support JPEG Check that thete is Warning in the test tool log Check that test tool will try to set jpeg for the first, middle anf last VECs DUT behaviour is correct: the last VEC will changed to the required encoding

Test.Name: One VEC supports JPEG: incorrect DUT behaviour
Test.Description: The second VEC supports JPEG Check that test tool will try to find/careate profile for the second VEC Incorrect DUT behaviour: profile for this VEC isn't found Check that test tool will not test the other VECs

Test.Name: Only one VEC exists and it doesn't support JPEG
Test.Description: Only one VEC exists on the DUT This VEC doesn't support JPEG Check that thete is Warning in the test tool log Check that test tool will try to set jpeg for this VEC DUT behaviour is correct
